[color=red][size=18]Spec Racer Ford Challenge Series @ [b] Mosport[/b]
Week 4 of 12 - 2018 Season 4 [/size][/color]
Race Distance: [b]15 laps[/b], approximately 25 minutes
World Record lap time: [b]1:32.766[/b] by Stian Svendsen (Qualifying)
(n.b. random/dynamic weather impacts lap times greatly)

Week 4 takes us back to Mosport (pronounced "moe-sport"), regularly visited by NASCAR series and more conventional road racers alike. This is a fast flowing track with a great rhythm and is great fun to race at.

Target "planned" SoF race is usually 20:45 GMT Sunday, immediately following the Weekend Warriors league race.

[img]http://members.iracing.com/jforum/posts/downloadAttach/2442836.page[/img]

